name: ISSfinder
0: ”Alexa, ask ISS finder where the ISS is at”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: i. s. s. finder
des: The ISS finder skill does one thing: it tracks the location of the International Space Station as it orbits the earth, second by second. Ask where the ISS is and you will get information regarding the country, state and municipality the space station is orbiting over, in realtime.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
